.SH NAME
gmc-task-webui - Start local kanban WebUI for tasks


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBgmc task webui [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Start a local HTTP server with a kanban WebUI for managing tasks in the current repository.

.PP
Opens your browser to a drag-and-drop task board. Attach uses Ghostty, iTerm2, or Terminal.app on macOS.


.SH OPTIONS
\fB-h\fP, \fB--help\fP[=false]
	help for webui


.SH OPTIONS INHERITED FROM PARENT COMMANDS
\fB--config\fP=""
	Config file (default: $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/gmc/config.yaml)

.PP
\fB--debug\fP[=false]
	Enable debug output

.PP
\fB-o\fP, \fB--output\fP="text"
	Output format: text or json


.SH EXAMPLE
.EX
  gmc task webui
.EE


.SH SEE ALSO
\fBgmc-task(1)\fP


